{"title":"单纯形大法好","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":0,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-6058","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个n维正单纯形，边长为m，求这个单纯形的n维超体积。</p><p>比如当n=3，m=1，棱长为1的正四面体体积为sqrt(2)/12。<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>一行两个整数n,m，中间用空格隔开<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一行一个二次根式或者有理数，表示超体积。二次根式应该格式化成asqrt(b)/c的格式，并且化到最简。有理数格式化成a/b。所有分母或者系数为1的必须省略。<br/></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>输入1：2 2</p><p>输入2：8 1<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>输出1：sqrt(3)</p><p>输出2：1/215040<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>保证所有在输出中出现的数字不超过long long的范围<br></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}